import React from 'react';
import { Box, Flex, Image, Button, Heading} from '@chakra-ui/react'
import money from '../images/money.png'; // using images with import


function HomePage() {
    return(
        <Box  
        background="linear-gradient(135deg, #D86FCC 0%, #01055B 100%)"
        border-radius="45px 45px 300px 45px"
        color="white"
        display='flex'
        alignItems='center'
        >
          <Box>
            <Heading as='h1' size='4xl'>
                Track your payments, balances, and dues between groups
            </Heading>
            <Button colorScheme='pink' size='md'>Get Started</Button> 
          </Box>
          <Box>
            <Image src={money}/>
          </Box>
        </Box>
    );
} 


export default HomePage;
